<para><verbatim>Members:

  Automatic : choose caching mode automatically depending on volume type
(current defaults: Normal for FunctionVolume and VdbVolume, None for others)

  None : don&apos;t cache any data

  Normal : allocates 2 full slices per parallel thread
</verbatim> </para>
